<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <title>Sidebar</title>
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body,
      html {
        height: 100%;
        font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #0a0a0a, rgb(125, 84, 175));
        overflow-x: hidden; /* Prevents horizontal scroll */
      }

      .gradient-bg {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        pointer-events: none;
        background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #0a0a0a, rgba(167, 119, 227, 1));

        z-index: -1;
        opacity: 0;
        transition: opacity 0.5s;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 20px;
        color: #f2f2f2;
        min-height: 110vh;
      }

      .text-container {
        margin: 40px auto 0 auto;
        max-width: 800px;
        text-align: center;
        animation: fadeIn 2s ease-in-out;
      }

      .text-container h1 {
        font-size: 3rem;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        letter-spacing: -0.5px;
      }

      .text-container p {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .awkward {
        color: #ff1d1d;
        font-weight: 700;
        animation: pulse 1.5s infinite;
      }

      .quote-container {
        margin-top: 50px;
      }

      .quote {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        font-style: italic;
        animation: fadeIn 3s ease-in-out;
      }

      .quote::before {
        content: "“";
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        vertical-align: top;
        color: #f2f2f2;
      }

      .quote::after {
        content: "”";
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        vertical-align: bottom;
        color: #f2f2f2;
      }

      .quote-author {
        text-align: right;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        color: rgba(242, 242, 242, 0.8);
      }

      .additional-message {
        margin-top: 50px;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        line-height: 1.5;
        text-align: center;
        animation: fadeInUp 2s ease-in-out;
      }

      @keyframes fadeIn {
        from {
          opacity: 0;
        }
        to {
          opacity: 1;
        }
      }

      @keyframes fadeInUp {
        from {
          opacity: 0;
          transform: translateY(20px);
        }
        to {
          opacity: 1;
          transform: translateY(0);
        }
      }

      @keyframes pulse {
        0% {
          transform: scale(1);
        }
        50% {
          transform: scale(1.1);
        }
        100% {
          transform: scale(1);
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .text-container h1 {
          font-size: 2.5rem;
        }
        .text-container p,
        .additional-message {
          font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
        .quote {
          font-size: 1.5rem;
        }
        .quote::before,
        .quote::after {
          font-size: 2rem;
        }
      }
    </style>
    <script>
      window.addEventListener("scroll", function () {
        const gradient = document.querySelector(".gradient-bg");
        const scrollTop = window.scrollY;
        const docHeight =
          document.documentElement.scrollHeight - window.innerHeight;
        const scrollPercent = scrollTop / docHeight;

        gradient.style.opacity = scrollPercent;
      });
    </script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('layout/sbar.ejs') %>
    <div class="gradient-bg"></div>
    <div class="content">
      <div class="text-container">
        <h1>Hi, user</h1>
        <p>
          Always Remember That You Are
          <br />
          <span class="awkward">Worthy.</span> <br />
        </p>
        <div class="quote-container">
          <p class="quote">. <%= quote %></p>
        </div>
        <div class="additional-message">
          <p>
            We will help you through a chatbot that will accompany you whenever
            you need someone to talk to tirelessly, and through a goal tracker
            that might help you focus on your strengths and strengthen them to
            make you realize how cool you are.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
